---
import {
    CardStories,
    CardStoriesAvatar,
    CardStoriesAvatarImage,
    CardStoriesName,
    CardStoriesText,
    CardStoriesQuote,
    quoteColors,
} from "@/components/ui/cardStories";
import StoriesCarousel from "@/components/react/StoriesCarousel";
---

<section class="py-8 md:py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-blue-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
        <!-- Desktop View - Grid Layout -->
        <div class="hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <CardStories className="h-full">
                <CardStoriesAvatar className="flex justify-center mb-4">
                    <CardStoriesAvatarImage src="/img/kid3.svg" alt="Shari" />
                </CardStoriesAvatar>
                <CardStoriesName className="comfortaa">
                    <span class="block">Hola,</span>
                    <span class="block">Soy Shari!</span>
                </CardStoriesName>
                <CardStoriesText>
                    "Nuestra biblioteca es pequeña, pero está llena de
                    esperanza. Con mi comunidad la construimos para que sea un
                    refugio de lectura. Necesitamos más libros educativos, que
                    nos preparen para la vida."
                </CardStoriesText>
                <CardStoriesQuote
                    color={quoteColors.cyan}
                    className="schoolbell">"Leer abre puertas"</CardStoriesQuote
                >
            </CardStories>

            <CardStories className="h-full">
                <CardStoriesAvatar className="flex justify-center mb-4">
                    <CardStoriesAvatarImage src="/img/kid2.svg" alt="Nayde" />
                </CardStoriesAvatar>
                <CardStoriesName className="comfortaa">
                    <span class="block">Hola,</span>
                    <span class="block">Soy Nayde!</span>
                </CardStoriesName>
                <CardStoriesText>
                    "Junto a mi comunidad construimos una biblioteca, un espacio
                    para aprender y soñar. Me gustaría tener libros de leyendas
                    de nuestra tierra y narraciones de historias."
                </CardStoriesText>
                <CardStoriesQuote
                    color={quoteColors.orange}
                    className="schoolbell">"Me encanta leer"</CardStoriesQuote
                >
            </CardStories>

            <CardStories className="h-full">
                <CardStoriesAvatar className="flex justify-center mb-4">
                    <CardStoriesAvatarImage src="/img/kid1.svg" alt="Alison" />
                </CardStoriesAvatar>
                <CardStoriesName className="comfortaa">
                    <span class="block">Hola,</span>
                    <span class="block">Soy Alison!</span>
                </CardStoriesName>
                <CardStoriesText>
                    "Con mis compañeros, profesores y padres de familia
                    construimos una biblioteca, un espacio para nosotros.
                    Queremos que la lectura nos ayude a prepararnos para el
                    futuro."
                </CardStoriesText>
                <CardStoriesQuote
                    color={quoteColors.green}
                    className="schoolbell">"Leer me relaja"</CardStoriesQuote
                >
            </CardStories>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile View - Carousel -->
        <div class="md:hidden py-4">
            <StoriesCarousel client:load />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .comfortaa {
        font-family: "Comfortaa Variable", "Comfortaa", sans-serif;
        font-variation-settings: "wght" 400;
    }

    .schoolbell {
        font-family: "Schoolbell", cursive;
        font-weight: 400;
        transform: rotate(-2deg);
        display: inline-block;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
</style>
